<L>__{interior ballroom night}
<A>__{music fills the air as the creme de la creme of victorian society gather inside. leopold holds a prearranged dance card. he looks at the names and finds his first partner is miss tree. leopold looks upward helplessly at an unrelenting god.}
<L>__{interior ballroom dance floor night}
<A>__{a profoundly self conscious leopold dances energetically into frame with miss tree, an ancient, elfin, yet amazingly spry woman who gapes up at him searchingly, unblinking. leopold opens his mouth to speak, can think of nothing suitable to say, and clamps his mouth shut. they dance out of frame.}
